Ek weet nie;	I don't know
Hy bid nooit;	He never prays
Weet jy dit nie?;	Don't you know that ?
Ek ken hom nie;	I don't know him
Geen mens weet nie;	No one knows
Ek ken nie daardie man nie;	I don't know that man
Jy let nie op nie;	You're not paying attention
Hy sal nie kom nie;	He won't come
Hy het nie gekom nie;	He hasn't come
Hy kom nie;	He doesn't come
Ek het nie geweet dat hy sou kom nie;	I didn't know that he would be coming
Ek het geweet dat hy nie sou kom nie;	I knew that he wouldn't be coming
Mense wat nie rook nie lewe langer;	People who don't smoke live longer
Hy kan nie kom nie want hy is siek;	He can't come because he is sick
Dis nie so moeilik om Afrikaans te leer nie;	It isn't so difficult to learn Afrikaans
Ek weet niks nie;	I know nothing
Hy skryf nooit nie;	He never writes
Ek ken niemand nie;	I don't know anyone


